title: ‘Ted Lasso’ Season 2 Finale Recap
description:
The Greyhound Gang review the eventful final episode of ‘Ted Lasso’ season 2, discuss its real-life parallels, and look ahead to where this show will go.
Host: Chris Ryan
Guest: Van Lathan
Producer: Isaac Lee
